- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper focuses on sorting algorithms, which is a fundamental topic in data structures and algorithms. 
- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture): The paper specifically targets the AVX-512 instruction set, which is a hardware architecture feature. 
- cs.PF (Performance): The paper reports on the performance study of the proposed algorithm, which is a key aspect of performance analysis. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper discusses the implementation of the algorithm and how it benefits from the new instructions, which is related to programming languages. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper describes a system-level approach to sorting using AVX-512, which could be relevant to the systems and control sub-category.
